      {
        "question": "How does billing work?",
        "answer": "Credits are deducted based on actual token usage. Each AI generation consumes credits proportional to the input and output tokens. You'll always see the credit cost before confirming a generation."
      },
      {
        "question": "Can I cancel my subscription anytime?",
        "answer": "Yes! You can cancel your subscription at any time from User Center > My Orders. Your credits will remain available until the end of the current billing period."
      },
